import React from "react"
function Login(){
    return (
        
      <form className="form">
   
      <Input
        type="text"
        placeholder="text"      
      />
      
      <Input
        type="passwor"
        placeholder="text"      
      />
      <button type="submit">Login</button>
    </form>
    )
}
export default Login;
